      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-36vm1 for review-dne-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/64749a98-e8f4-44c6-b7a4-5903c6f1dc8c). Ran 16 tests. No failures.",
